text: Hi all! I am currently running into an issue with a landing page & HubDB. The LP is a dynamic page that is populated via a HubDB table as the data source. The error that I am getting is "HubDB Table [table #] is already over the limit of 10 dynamic pages per HubDB table". The page has been published previously, but will no longer allow for publishing any updates. Can someone help me determine the issue here and is there a solve for this or workaround?
That means the HubDB table is being used on over 10 pages. Why are you using the same HubDB table to generate dynamic pages on so many parent pages?
